{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To predict learning outcomes, the study used student's interactions in seven general preparation courses presented on Blackboard.",
    "Mixed-methods were utilized that included four DL models, and the best prediction was achieved with CNN-LSTM compared with CNN, RNN, LSTM, and CNN-RNN.",
    "The reason behind this is the selection of many factors that affect DL models which then influence the prediction accuracy and prediction error, including the size of the CNN convolution filter, the number of neurons in the LSTM, and the size of the LSTM batch.",
    "A student performance prediction model named (GDPN) was proposed by Liu et al (2022c).",
    "The model simultaneously extracts temporal information and general information about student's learning behaviors."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "A student performance prediction model named (GDPN) was proposed by Liu et al (2022c)."
  ]
}